937), documenting his experience of working-class life in the industrial north of England, and Homage to Catalonia (1938), an account of his experiences soldiering for the Republican faction of the Spanish Civil War (1936–1939), are as critically respected as his essays on politics, literature, language and culture.\u003cbr /\u003eOrwell's work remains influential in popular culture and in political culture, and the adjective \"Orwellian\"—describing totalitarian and authoritarian social practices—is part of the English language, like many of his neologisms, such as \"Big Brother\", \"Thought Police\", \"Room 101\", \"Newspeak\", \"memory hole\", \"doublethink\", and \"thoughtcrime\". In 2008, The Times named Orwell the second-greatest British writer since 1945.","isGrAuthor":false,"works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":1171},"profileImageUrl":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1588856560i/3706._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/3706.George_Orwell","user":null,"viewerIsFollowing":null,"followers":{"__typename":"ContributorFollowersConnection","totalCount":47332}},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v3.Emy23xgDnXpqF2NP":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v3.Emy23xgDnXpqF2NP","__typename":"Book","legacyId":61439040,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/61439040-1984"},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.SgJQSc4-cyFNY1JLB6R9mA":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.SgJQSc4-cyFNY1JLB6R9mA","__typename":"Work","legacyId":153313,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v3.Emy23xgDnXpqF2NP"},"choiceAwards":[],"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/153313-nineteen-eighty-four","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/153313-nineteen-eighty-four","publicationTime":-649008000000,"originalTitle":"Nineteen Eighty-Four","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Prometheus Hall of Fame Award","webUrl":"https://www.goodrea